[{'text': "Today I'm going to repair a broken garage
door hinge, actually I have 2 broken hinges", 'start': 0.81, 'duration': 4.43}, {'text': "I need to fix and I've never done this before.
But at the end of this video, you'll be able", 'start': 5.24, 'duration': 3.97}, {'text': 'to do this repair on your own and save a lot
of money.', 'start': 9.21, 'duration': 3.35}, {'text': "The hinges I'm repairing are ones that are
next to the track on the ends of the garage", 'start': 12.56, 'duration': 4.42}, {'text': 'door. As you can see, this hinge has completely
snapped.', 'start': 16.98, 'duration': 4.42}, {'text': 'So the first thing you need to do is disengage
the door from the motor and then roll the', 'start': 21.4, 'duration': 3.959}, {'text': "door all the way down.
Replacement hinges can be found at Lowe's", 'start': 25.359, 'duration': 6.64}, {'text': "which is where I got mine but you can probably
find them at any big hardware store. The one's", 'start': 31.999, 'duration': 4.451}, {'text': 'I bought were only $5.00 each. One thing you
will need to pay attention to is the number', 'start': 36.45, 'duration': 4.09}, {'text': 'on the package. I bought the number one hinges.
Each hinge position has a different number', 'start': 40.54, 'duration': 6.06}, {'text': 'as you can see from my door. It starts with
number one down at the bottom and then goes', 'start': 46.6, 'duration': 3.83}, {'text': 'up to number three. Taller doors may have higher
numbers than 3.', 'start': 50.43, 'duration': 5.12}, {'text': "That's because the track actually sits closer
to the door frame at the bottom than at the", 'start': 55.55, 'duration': 4.03}, {'text': 'top of the frame. The hinges above number
one offset the rollers from the track so that', 'start': 59.58, 'duration': 5.81}, {'text': 'the door will sit flush when completely closed.
And if you happen to buy the wrong number', 'start': 65.39, 'duration': 4.93}, {'text': "hinge, don't worry about it. The cylinder
in the middle of all the hinges line up with", 'start': 70.32, 'duration': 3.839}, {'text': 'the number one hinge as you can see here.
And the top and bottom roller brackets are', 'start': 74.159, 'duration': 7.0}, {'text': 'totally different from the hinges.
So now that you know a little about garage', 'start': 81.429, 'duration': 4.271}, {'text': "hinges, let's start replacing the broken ones.
I'll start by removing bolts from the bottom of the hinge and work my way up.", 'start': 85.7, 'duration': 13.0}, {'text': '--Drill Sounds--', 'start': 99.6, 'duration': 2.039}, {'text': "Now just slide the roller out and keep it handy, we'll reuse that part again.
And here's our shiny new hinge ready to be", 'start': 131.25, 'duration': 4.68}, {'text': "installed.
I'll do this all in reverse order starting", 'start': 135.93, 'duration': 2.809}, {'text': 'with the roller. Just slip it in the track
and slide the hinge over it like this.', 'start': 138.739, 'duration': 5.401}, {'text': 'Now line up the holes with the openings in
the hinge and then place the bolts back in', 'start': 144.14, 'duration': 3.47}, {'text': "starting from the top. And don't forget to
use the washer from the old hinge.", 'start': 147.61, 'duration': 7.0}, {'text': 'Once all the bolts are back in and the hinge
is nice and tight, I can start working on the other side now.', 'start': 210.629, 'duration': 7.0}, {'text': '--MUSIC and DRILL SOUNDS--', 'start': 220.6, 'duration': 7.0}, {'text': "Ok so the second hinge is done and as youcan see, it isn't too hard to replace and I think anyone who's even slightly handy can", 'start': 269.43, 'duration': 4.51}, {'text': "do it. And as I said in the beginning of the
video, I've never done this before and was", 'start': 273.94, 'duration': 4.43}, {'text': 'still able to make the repair easily.
So now the last thing to do is re-engage the', 'start': 278.37, 'duration': 4.78}, {'text': "door to the motor and you're all set!
If you enjoyed this tutorial, please subscribe.", 'start': 283.15, 'duration': 5.329}, {'text': "I've got lots more product reviews and tutorials
like this one coming up!", 'start': 288.479, 'duration': 7.0}]

[{'text': "In this video you'll see how to create the leaves for your origami willow bonsai.", 'start': 1.834, 'duration': 6.522}, {'text': 'Start with a couple different sizes of paper.', 'start': 8.356, 'duration': 2.441}, {'text': "Here we've got a one inch by two inch piece, and a three quarter inch by one and a half inches.", 'start': 10.797, 'duration': 6.223}, {'text': 'These are both made out of tissue foil.', 'start': 17.02, 'duration': 3.808}, {'text': 'Take the paper fold it in half to create a center line.', 'start': 20.828, 'duration': 5.618}, {'text': 'This acts as a point of reference for the rest of your folds.', 'start': 26.446, 'duration': 5.721}, {'text': 'Take the corner, fold it from the center line so that the tip reaches over to the far side.', 'start': 32.167, 'duration': 8.624}, {'text': 'and then crease along until you come to about the same distance from the top of the paper', 'start': 40.791, 'duration': 8.998}, {'text': 'as from the  top to the center line, so it forms a square in the top corner. And do the same for the other side.', 'start': 49.789, 'duration': 12.841}, {'text': 'Folding across from the center line, and then fold the overlap over to the other side.', 'start': 62.63, 'duration': 10.897}, {'text': 'So this creates the stem part of your leaf.', 'start': 73.527, 'duration': 4.619}, {'text': 'Now create a little crease just below where the first folds meet the side of the paper.', 'start': 78.146, 'duration': 8.323}, {'text': 'And then fold from the center fold over so that the tip is about half way across to the opposite side.', 'start': 86.469, 'duration': 12.407}, {'text': 'And fold the other tip down so that it meets the fold of the previous tip.', 'start': 98.876, 'duration': 6.885}, {'text': 'Like that.', 'start': 105.761, 'duration': 3.35}, {'text': "And then the new tip that's formed, fold it over into the center, to form the top part of your leaf.", 'start': 109.111, 'duration': 13.303}, {'text': 'Now to make the stem, you want to fold the bottom third, up towards the top,', 'start': 122.414, 'duration': 8.228}, {'text': 'so that the tip ends up about half way between the fold and the top of the leaf.', 'start': 130.642, 'duration': 6.518}, {'text': 'Then fold it back, and create a little indent underneath the fold, like this.', 'start': 137.16, 'duration': 12.615}, {'text': 'And then crimp it together.', 'start': 149.775, 'duration': 5.45}, {'text': 'Then take your finger nail and crease the center of the stem.', 'start': 155.225, 'duration': 6.548}, {'text': 'And then pinch it while at the same time pressing down on the top part of the leaf.', 'start': 161.773, 'duration': 9.032}, {'text': 'and then do a little shaping to round the leaf a little bit.', 'start': 170.805, 'duration': 4.413}, {'text': 'And there your go.', 'start': 175.218, 'duration': 359823.782}]

[{'text': 'Hi, Im Matthew Tomaszewski of the College of Liberal Arts and Sciences ', 'start': 24.892, 'duration': 2.335}, {'text': 'at the University of Illinois. Welcome to This Old Hall, ', 'start': 27.528, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'the story of the renovation of one of the most historically significant ', 'start': 30.952, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'and highly used classroom buildings on campus. ', 'start': 33.483, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'This month were taking a look at the work ', 'start': 37.105, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'that was done on Lincoln Hall over the summer.  ', 'start': 38.475, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'Its been a busy time, and despite record temperatures, ', 'start': 40.474, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'a productive one.', 'start': 43.259, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'The three words that best describe the work done this summer:', 'start': 45.232, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'demolition, demolition, demolition.', 'start': 47.02, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'The goals for the renovation of Lincoln Hall ', 'start': 51.0, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'are to preserve its historical elements ', 'start': 53.021, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'while creating a modern, energy efficient', 'start': 55.426, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'learning environment. ', 'start': 57.257, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'Thus, the early stages of the project have involved ', 'start': 59.629, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'protecting or removing historically significant features. ', 'start': 61.394, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'For instance, last spring, contractors removed', 'start': 64.11, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'dozens of doors and over 5,000 feet of wood trim, ', 'start': 66.432, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'which have been carefully wrapped and', 'start': 70.055, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'sent off for refinishing.
